# Regenerable 2x screenshot masters. The shipped store images (store-assets/*.jpg,
# *.png) are committed; these high-res intermediates are rebuilt on demand from the
# Store/Screenshots stories via headless capture, so they stay out of history.
apps/extension/store-assets/masters/

